snippet.title: Johnny Depp Thanks Amber Heard For 'Putting Up With Him'!
snippet.description:
"Johnny Depp thanked his wife Amber Heard for ""putting up"" with him and the multiple characters he had played on-screen.

Johnny Depp is an American actor, producer, and musician. He has won the Golden Globe Award and Screen Actors Guild Award for Best Actor. He rose to prominence on the 1980s television series 21 Jump Street, becoming a teen idol.

Amber Heard is an American actress, who made her film debut in the acclaimed sports drama Friday Night Lights. After small roles in North Country and Alpha Dog, she played her first leading role in All the Boys Love Mandy Lane and appeared in The CW television show Hidden Palms.
